headline: 3D Energi Runs Out of Cash for Victoria Drill Campaign, Suspends Trading
summary: 3D Energi has voluntarily halted trading on the Australian Securities Exchange, having defaulted on the payment of its share of costs in a ConocoPhillips-led exploration campaign in the Otway basin offshore Victoria.
